+// О“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГү UPLOAD LOGIC О“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГүО“ГІГү
+async function handlePDFFileSelect(file, dropzoneId, targetLinkInputId) {
+    if (!file || file.type !== 'application/pdf') {
+        alert("Veuillez sв”ңвҢҗlectionner un fichier PDF valide.");
+        return;
+    }
+    await uploadPDFToSupabase(file, dropzoneId, targetLinkInputId);
+}
+
+async function handlePDFDrop(event, dropzoneId, targetLinkInputId) {
+    event.preventDefault();
+    document.getElementById(dropzoneId).style.borderColor = 'var(--line)';
+    
+    if (event.dataTransfer.items) {
+        var item = event.dataTransfer.items[0];
+        if (item.kind === 'file') {
+            var file = item.getAsFile();
+            if (file && file.type === 'application/pdf') {
+                await uploadPDFToSupabase(file, dropzoneId, targetLinkInputId);
+                return;
+            }
+        }
+    }
+    alert("Veuillez glisser un fichier PDF valide.");
+}
+
+async function uploadPDFToSupabase(file, dropzoneId, targetLinkInputId) {
+    var label = document.getElementById(dropzoneId + '-label');
+    var progress = document.getElementById(dropzoneId + '-progress');
+    
+    label.style.display = 'none';
+    progress.style.display = 'block';
+    progress.style.color = '#60a5fa'; // Blue
+    progress.textContent = 'Envoi vers Medflix Serveur...';
+    
+    try {
+        var cleanName = file.name.replace(/[^a-zA-Z0-9.\-_]/g, '_');
+        var fileName = Date.now() + '_' + cleanName;
+        
+        var { data, error } = await sb.storage.from('medflix-pdfs').upload(fileName, file, {
+            cacheControl: '3600',
+            upsert: false
+        });
+        
+        if (error) {
+            console.error(error);
+            progress.style.color = '#f87171'; // Red
+            progress.innerHTML = "Erreur : " + error.message + "<br><span style='font-size:0.7rem;color:var(--mut2);'>(Avez-vous crв”ңвҢҗв”ңвҢҗ le bucket 'medflix-pdfs' et activв”ңвҢҗ les politiques d'insertion/lecture ?)</span>";
+            setTimeout(function(){ label.style.display = 'block'; progress.style.display = 'none'; }, 8000);
+            return;
+        }
+        
+        // Generate exact public URL
+        var { data: publicUrlData } = sb.storage.from('medflix-pdfs').getPublicUrl(fileName);
+        
+        // Fill the input
+        document.getElementById(targetLinkInputId).value = publicUrlData.publicUrl;
+        
+        progress.style.color = '#4ade80';
+        progress.textContent = 'О“ВЈГ  Fichier uploadв”ңвҢҗ avec succв”ңВҝs et lien rempli !';
+        setTimeout(function(){ label.style.display = 'block'; progress.style.display = 'none'; }, 4000);
+        
+    } catch(err) {
+        console.error("Upload exception", err);
+        progress.style.color = '#f87171';
+        progress.textContent = "Une erreur serveur inattendue est survenue.";
+        setTimeout(function(){ label.style.display = 'block'; progress.style.display = 'none'; }, 4000);
+    }
+}
